      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1779151224535,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional Requirements\nIn Scope\n- Start group chats\n- send/receive messages\n- send/receive media\n- Access messages after I've been offline\n\nOut of Scope\n- Audio Call\n- Video call\n\n\nNon-functional requirments\nConstraints\n- Delivered with low latency -> <500ms\n- Data Retention policy\n\nQualities\n- Guarantee delivery of messages\n- High throughput\n- Fault-tolerant\n\nScale\n- Scalability -> 1B users\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional Requirements\nIn Scope\n- Start group chats\n- send/receive messages\n- send/receive media\n- Access messages after I've been offline\n\nOut of Scope\n- Audio Call\n- Video call\n\n\nNon-functional requirments\nConstraints\n- Delivered with low latency -> <500ms\n- Data Retention policy\n\nQualities\n- Guarantee delivery of messages\n- High throughput\n- Fault-tolerant\n\nScale\n- Scalability -> 1B users\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
